                "text": "<p><span class=\"light-font\"><span class=\"body-unica-32-reg\">From strong corporate governance, to the highest standards in quality, compliance, safety and performance, we strive to always do the right thing.</span></span><br>&#xd;&#xa;</p>&#xd;&#xa;"
