          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text-container-text",
              "props": {
                "text": "<p>To make a positive, long-term impact for patients, we earn and maintain their trust by acting with integrity in everything we do. We pride ourselves on our unwavering principles and our commitment, knowing not only is it the right thing to do, but it also ensures the resiliency of our business and our long-term success. </p>&#xd;&#xa;"
